		<p>ArtYam helps artists sell more art in non-gallery venues like cafes, retail shops, restaurants, banks, hospitals, etc.  ArtYam puts artists in control of their marketing in any venue by giving them the tools to directly engage art collectors with information about themselves and their artwork through online tear sheets.  ArtYam also provides payment processing capabilities that enable art collectors to instantly buy an artist's work online commission-free.</p>

